**To-Do List**  
A task management tool designed with women in STEM in mind.

Software engineering and web development remain male-dominated fields. This project was created to provide a task management tool that celebrates and supports women pursuing careers in STEM, featuring a pink-themed, friendly interface that breaks away from traditional tech aesthetics.

**Tech Stack**

* JavaScript  
* HTML  
* CSS

**Getting Started**  
Open \`index.html\` in your browser to start managing your tasks\!
